# Commit and push on every paper change

After any coherent set of edits to this repository (sections, main.tex, cover letter, supplementary, README, figures), **commit and push to `origin`** without waiting for a separate request.

**`origin` is the personal fork:** `YMJ1123/gfm-metagenomic-benchmark-paper`  
(not `m2lab-ntu/...` — that remote is `upstream` only).

Use HEREDOC / `-F` commit messages; do not force-push; do not amend unless the usual amend conditions are met.
